1
03:05:26,741 --> 03:05:28,075
What was that?

2
03:05:28,868 --> 03:05:31,245
- What happened?
- It fell. I saw it.

3
03:05:34,649 --> 03:05:35,684
It's dead.

4
03:05:40,046 --> 03:05:41,380
Smaug is dead.

5
03:05:42,256 --> 03:05:45,593
GLOIN:
By my beard, I think he's right.

6
03:05:46,010 --> 03:05:47,386
Look there!

7
03:05:48,228 --> 03:05:49,229
[RAVENS CAWING]

8
03:05:49,480 --> 03:05:53,192
The Ravens of Erebor
are returning to the Mountain.

9
03:05:54,360 --> 03:05:55,027
BALIN:
Aye.

10
03:05:55,277 --> 03:05:56,737
Word will spread.

11
03:05:56,987 --> 03:06:00,908
Before long every soul
in Middle-earth will know...

12
03:06:01,158 --> 03:06:03,243
...the dragon is dead!

13
03:06:04,495 --> 03:06:06,495
[DWARVES LAUGHING]

